<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Agriculture Supervisor 2026 - Strategy</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0d11;
            --card-bg: #161b22;
            --accent-gold: #d4af37;
            --text-white: #f0f6fc;
            --text-gray: #8b949e;
            --danger: #ff4d4d;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-white);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-gold);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .reality-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
        }

        .stat-card span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .negative { color: var(--danger) !important; }

        .section-title {
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            color: black;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .plan-box {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1c2128, #161b22);
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-gold);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .plan-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
        }

        .topics-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .topic-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .topic-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .topic-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-gold);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: var(--text-gray);
        }

        li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>AGRI SUPERVISOR 2026</h1>
        <p>Target: 100 MCQs | 300 Marks</p>
    </header>

    <div class="reality-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <p>Time</p>
            <span>2 Hours</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <p>Negative</p>
            <span class="negative">-1/3 Mark</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <p>Agriculture</p>
            <span>60 Qs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <p>Hindi/GK</p>
            <span>40 Qs</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">1-DAY PASS STRATEGY</div>
    <div class="plan-box">
        <p><strong>🧠 Rule:</strong> RATTA + REPEATED TOPICS + MCQ PRACTICE</p>
        <div class="plan-item"><span>4 Hours</span> <strong>Agriculture (Core)</strong></div>
        <div class="plan-item"><span>2 Hours</span> <strong>Rajasthan GK</strong></div>
        <div class="plan-item"><span>1 Hour</span> <strong>Hindi</strong></div>
        <div class="plan-item"><span>2 Hours</span> <strong>MCQ Revision</strong></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">MOST REPEATED TOPICS</div>
    <div class="topics-container">
        <div class="topic-card">
            <h3>🌾 Agronomy</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Crop Rotation & Systems</li>
                <li>Irrigation Methods</li>
                <li>Fertilizers (NPK usage)</li>
                <li>Soil Types (Alluvial, Black, Red)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card">
            <h3>🌱 Horticulture</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Fruit Crops: Mango, Citrus, Guava</li>
                <li>Propagation: Cutting & Grafting</li>
                <li>Nursery Management</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card">
            <h3>🐄 Animal Husbandry</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Breeds: Gir, Sahiwal, Buffalo types</li>
                <li>Milk Production & Composition</li>
                <li>Diseases: FMD, Mastitis</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Focus on the high-yield topics. Best of luck for April 18!</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
